g-more-games-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/disney-illusion-island-developer-making-more-games-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/disney-illusion-island-developer-making-more-games-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/disney-illusion-island-developer-making-more-games-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/disney-illusion-island-developer-making-more-games-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/disney-illusion-island"><em>《迪士尼幻觉岛》</em></a>的开发商 Dlala Studios 的首席执行官表示，该团队将抓住机会制作多款<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/disney">迪士尼</a>游戏。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/disney-illusion-island-preview-diala-studios-3439195">迪士尼幻觉岛看起来像是一剂怀旧之情</a></strong></li></ul><p>在接受<em><a href="https://www.techradar.com/gaming/disney-illusion-islands-developer-on-creating-a-spiritual-successor-to-a-sega-classic-and-whats-next" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tech Radar Gaming</a></em>采访时，AJ Grand-Scrutton 谈到了他和 IT 总监 Mark Ragon 仍然对<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/sega-mega-drive">Sega Mega Drive</a>上的原版<em>《Castle Of Illusion Starring Mickey Mouse》</em>和<em>《World Of Illusion》</em>游戏的热爱。</p><p> “如果没有这些游戏，这款游戏就不会存在，”他解释道，并扩展了《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/ori-and-the-will-of-the-wisps"><em>Ori》</em></a>系列、《<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/metroid"><em>银河战士》</em></a>游戏和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/devolver-acquires-gunbrella-developer-doinksoft-3425671"><em>《Gato Roboto》</em></a>等最近对<em>迪士尼幻觉岛的</em>影响。</p><p>未来，游戏是否会有可下载内容（DLC），例如米奇、米妮、唐老鸭和高飞以外的新可玩角色，还有待观察。尽管如此，Grand-Scruton 似乎对与迪士尼的合作非常积极，并且已经想到了 Dlala Studios 下一步可以创造什么。</p><p> “有一个清单。我们喜欢做知识产权方面的事情。我们喜欢利用现有的世界并用它们做一些新的事情。我们列出了我们希望利用的十大知识产权，”首席执行官说道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3478362" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3478362" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3478362" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/disney-illusion-island-developer-making-more-games-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/disney-illusion-island-developer-making-more-games-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/disney-illusion-island-developer-making-more-games-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/disney-illusion-island-developer-making-more-games-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/disney-illusion-island-developer-making-more-games-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/disney-illusion-island-developer-making-more-games-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/disney-illusion-island-developer-making-more-games-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3478362" class="wp-caption-text"> “迪士尼幻觉岛”图片来源：迪士尼互动</figcaption></figure><p>“在过去的几年里，名单上的东西越来越多地归迪士尼所有！所以有很多事情，这对迪士尼来说并不意外。他们听到我们提出了很多想法，”Grand-Scruton 继续说道。 “团队中有一些成员愿意制作一款新的唐老鸭游戏，无论是《 <em>QuackShot》、《Maui Mallard》、《Duck Tales》</em>还是《 <em>Darkwing Duck》</em> 。</p><p> “但对我来说，显然我喜欢这款游戏《<em>迪士尼幻觉岛》</em> ，并且有一天制作这款游戏​​续集的想法让我兴奋不已。据我们所知，迪士尼和我们一样喜欢这种关系，所以我不想透露太多，以防有一天这些成为现实，而我破坏了给你的惊喜！</p><p> “我想说的是，我们都很高兴与迪士尼长期合作，”首席执行官总结道。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，据报道，社交媒体上出现了一款<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/new-lego-harry-potter-game-seen-on-social-media-claims-report-3478306">新的<em>乐高哈利波特</em>游戏</a>，可能采用<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/lego-star-wars-the-skywalker-saga-review-a-cosmic-toybox-full-of-charm-3197656">乐高星球大战：天行者传奇</a></em>的风格。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/disney-illusion-island-developer-has-a-list-of-potential-disney-games-to-make-3478341">《迪士尼幻觉岛》的开发商发布了一份潜在迪士尼游戏的“清单”，这些游戏将</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《最终幻想 14》混合曲由 200 名音乐家演奏超过十年的主题https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/final-fantasy-14-medley-has-200-musicians-play-over-a-decade-of-themes-3478318?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=最终幻想 14 混合曲有 200 名音乐家演奏了十年的主题Imogen DonovanFri, 04 Aug 2023 13:05:34 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3478318 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/final-fantasy-14-medley-200-musicians.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/final-fantasy-14-medley-200-musicians.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/final-fantasy-14-medley-200-musicians-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/final-fantasy-14-medley-200-musicians-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/final-fantasy-14-medley-200-musicians-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/final-fantasy-14-medley-200-musicians-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/final-fantasy-14-medley-200-musicians-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>未来还会有更多的混合比赛</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/final-fantasy-14-medley-has-200-musicians-play-over-a-decade-of-themes-3478318">《最终幻想 14》后的混合曲由 200 名音乐家演奏了十多年的主题，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/final-fantasy-14-medley-200-musicians.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/final-fantasy-14-medley-200-musicians.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/final-fantasy-14-medley-200-musicians-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/final-fantasy-14-medley-200-musicians-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/final-fantasy-14-medley-200-musicians-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/final-fantasy-14-medley-200-musicians-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/final-fantasy-14-medley-200-musicians-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>超过十年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/final-fantasy-xiv"><em>《最终幻想 14》</em></a>主题已被 200 名粉丝和音乐家编排成混合曲，作为写给这款大型多人在线角色扮演游戏的情书。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/guides/gaming-guides/best-rpg-games-2974129">2023 年您可以玩的最佳角色扮演游戏</a></strong></li></ul><p>Masayoshi Soken 为这款深受喜爱的游戏创作的作品由 Husky by the Geek 编织而成，每个扩展包的主题在表演中都有自己的部分。看看下面： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="200 名音乐家的《最终幻想 XIV》10 年混合曲" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/h2s1NrBQjFM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>它从<em>《重生之境》</em>开始，然后是《苍穹之禁城》，“从天堂<em>撕裂</em>”变成“轨迹”，然后又变成“残酷正义”。 Rak&#39;tika Greatwood 的主题“文明”也经过了重制， <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aBt4zT_PBmw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2021 年 Soken 的 otamatone 翻唱让粉丝们深深地记住了这一主题</a>。所有 200 名音乐家和歌手的名单均在视频评论中注明。</p><p> “当我开始使用 YouTube 时，我一直梦想着能够参与这样的社区合作。现在我是这个活动的组织者，我希望我能通过玩让人们开心！”极客哈士奇说道，并保证未来还会有更多混合泳。 “我在编排这首歌并分配适合每个人的部分时感到很有趣，这样人们无论水平如何都可以加入。”</p><p>在其他地方， <em>《最终幻想 14》</em>的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/final-fantasy-14-dawntrail-expansion-and-xbox-version-announced-3475455">《黎明之路》</a></em>资料片也在今年的粉丝节上进行了展示，其中以新的热带地区图拉尔为特色。新的枢纽城市是图利约拉尔 (Tuliyollal)，位于约克图拉尔 (Yok Tural) 北部。当他们到达时，光之战士和子孙们面临着马穆尔贾下一任领袖继承权的冲突。</p><p>此外，还宣布该游戏将于 2024 年初登陆<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a> ，并在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-x">Xbox Series X</a>上支持 4K。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，据称<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/warner-bros">华纳兄弟</a>社交媒体帐户<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/new-lego-harry-potter-game-seen-on-social-media-claims-report-3478306">泄露了一款新的乐高哈利波特游戏</a>，这证实了今年早些时候的报道。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/final-fantasy-14-medley-has-200-musicians-play-over-a-decade-of-themes-3478318">《最终幻想 14》后的混合曲由 200 名音乐家演奏了十多年的主题，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
托马斯·班加特 (Thomas Bangalter) 对愚蠢朋克的结束感到“松了口气” https://www.nme.com/news/music/thomas-bangalter-relieved-over-way-daft-punk-ending-3478342?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=thomas-bangalter-relieved-over-way-daft-朋克结尾Liberty DunworthFri, 04 Aug 2023 12:39:25 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronicPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3478342 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Daft-Punk-Header-David-Black.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="傻朋克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Daft-Punk-Header-David-Black.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Daft-Punk-Header-David-Black-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Daft-Punk-Header-David-Black-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Daft-Punk-Header-David-Black-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Daft-Punk-Header-David-Black-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Daft-Punk-Header-David-Black-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们没有把事情搞砸太多”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thomas-bangalter-relieved-over-way-daft-punk-ended-3478342">托马斯·班加特 (Thomas Bangalter) 因《愚蠢朋克》的结束而“松了一口气”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Daft-Punk-Header-David-Black.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="傻朋克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Daft-Punk-Header-David-Black.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Daft-Punk-Header-David-Black-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Daft-Punk-Header-David-Black-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Daft-Punk-Header-David-Black-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Daft-Punk-Header-David-Black-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Daft-Punk-Header-David-Black-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daft-punk">Daft Punk</a>成员托马斯·班<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thomas-bangalter">加特 (Thomas Bangalter)</a>透露，他对乐队的结束感到“松了口气”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/daniel-vangarde-interview-2022-daft-punk-thomas-bangalter-does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-3370321">傻朋克的持久影响：“他们表现出了这种不在乎的态度”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位与 Guy-Manuel de Homem-Christo 共同创立了法国电子二人组的音乐家在接受新采访时回顾了自己在乐队中的时光，并回忆了自己<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/daft-punk-confirm-their-split-after-28-years-2886037">在 2021 年退出乐队时</a>的感受。</p><p>在与<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/m0017kqb" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BBC 广播 6 音乐</a>频道的讨论中，Bangalter 解释说，结束该项目“感觉很好”，有时也会对 Daft Punk 在 1997 年首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/daft-punk-release-25th-anniversary-edition-of-debut-album-3167260">“Homework”</a>之后继续创作音乐的时间感到惊讶。</p><p>在被问及为什么他们决定分道扬镳后，他说：“我自己问的更多的问题是我们为什么要结束它，而不是它如何能持续这么久。” “这很像一个故事或迷你传奇——有时有一个电视节目在人们心中占有特殊的位置，并且会保留这个位置，并且会播放一季、两季、三季、四季、五季，有时甚至是十季。</p><p> “有一个结束的时刻，我认为有这个机会开始、中间和结束实际上很有趣……[我]松了一口气，很高兴回顾过去说：‘好吧，我们没有搞砸。涨太多了。’” </p><figure id="attachment_3415430" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3415430" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3415430" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Daft-Punk@2000x1270.jpg" alt="傻朋克" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Daft-Punk@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Daft-Punk@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Daft-Punk@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Daft-Punk@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Daft-Punk@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Daft-Punk@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3415430" class="wp-caption-text">愚蠢的朋克。图片来源：Kevork Djansezian/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在采访的其他地方，他还深入了解了他们在创办 Daft Punk 时匿名背后的原因，并解释了他们选择戴上标志性面具的原因。</p><p> “当你 25 岁左右的时候，你就有了一个想法，[但是]你不会说‘你知道吗？我们要打扮得像机器人，直到死的那一天……&#39;,</p><p> “我真的记得当时的想法——让好莱坞的特效人员来扮演这些角色会很有趣——机器人角色就像是星球大战中小酒馆场景的一部分或类似的东西，”他补充道。 “这是一个奇怪的想法，我和盖曼都没有想到它最终会占据如此大的比例。”</p><p>在 4 月份的一次单独采访中，Bangalter 再次探讨了乐队于 2021 年退出的原因，透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/daft-punks-thomas-bangalter-explains-the-reason-for-their-split-3425585">他想与受技术启发的声音保持距离</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3386041" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3386041" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3386041" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Thomas-Bangalter-Credit-Stephane-Manel.jpg" alt="托马斯·班高特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Thomas-Bangalter-Credit-Stephane-Manel.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Thomas-Bangalter-Credit-Stephane-Manel-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Thomas-Bangalter-Credit-Stephane-Manel-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Thomas-Bangalter-Credit-Stephane-Manel-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Thomas-Bangalter-Credit-Stephane-Manel-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Thomas-Bangalter-Credit-Stephane-Manel-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3386041" class="wp-caption-text">托马斯·班加特.图片来源：斯蒂芬·马内尔。</figcaption></figure><p> “我喜欢技术作为一种工具，但我对机器与我们之间关系的本质感到恐惧，”他说。 “现在故事已经结束了，揭示部分创作过程感觉很有趣，它很大程度上是基于人类的，而不是任何类型的算法。”</p><p>分手后，Bangalter 宣布了他二十多年来的第一张个人专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/daft-punks-thomas-bangalter-announces-new-solo-album-mythologies-3386001">《Mythologies》</a> ，该专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/daft-punk-thomas-bangalter-scoring-new-ballet-3007817">最初被构思为芭蕾舞配乐</a>，并于去年七月在波尔多的波尔多大剧院演出。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thomas-bangalter-relieved-over-way-daft-punk-ended-3478342">托马斯·班加特 (Thomas Bangalter) 因《愚蠢朋克》的结束而“松了一口气”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 《继承之战》主演莎拉·斯努克解释了为什么希夫投票反对肯德尔https://www.nme.com/news/tv/succession-star-sarah-snook-explains-why-shiv-voted-against-kendall-3478313?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=succession-star-sarah-snook-解释了为什么希夫投票反对肯德尔Chris EdwardsFri, 04 Aug 2023 12:09:44 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3478313 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="继任结局" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我认为这是一个触发反应”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/succession-star-sarah-snook-explains-why-shiv-voted-against-kendall-3478313">《继承之战》明星莎拉·斯努克 (Sarah Snook) 解释了为什么希夫投票反对肯德尔 (Kendall)</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="继任结局" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/succession"><em>Succession</em></a> star Sarah Snook has explained what she believed prompted Shiv to vote against Jeremy Strong&#39;s Kendall in the <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/hbo">HBO</a> show&#39;s series finale.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/how-old-was-logan-roy-when-he-died-in-succession-3440098">How old was Logan Roy when he died in &#39;Succession&#39;?</a></strong></li></ul><p> In an interview with <a href="https://variety.com/2023/tv/news/succession-sarah-snook-tom-wambsgans-ceo-finale-1235684841/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a> , the actor suggested that Shiv decided to sabotage Kendall&#39;s chances of taking control of media conglomerate Waystar Royco after seeing her brother put his feet up on the desk of their late father, Logan (Brian Cox).</p><p> Shiv&#39;s decision ultimately left the company in the hands of Alexander Skarsgård&#39;s tech mogul Lukas Matsson, while her husband and the father of her unborn child, Tom Wambsgans (Matthew Macfadyen), assumed the role of CEO.</p><p> “I&#39;ve spoken with friends of mine who love the show, and I quite like being able to dissect it with them,” said Snook in the interview. “I have heard that people thought that Shiv was thinking 10 steps ahead, and that if Tom&#39;s going to get the CEO-ship and she&#39;s got a kid with Tom, then the closest she can be to it is by saying &#39;No&#39; [to Kendall] in this moment.</p><p> “But I think it&#39;s just pure instinct,” she continued. “I think it&#39;s a trigger response. It&#39;s scratching an open wound that is always there with the siblings. And this was in the script in the big print — when she sees Kendall put his feet up on Dad&#39;s desk? There&#39;s something in her that goes like, &#39;Ahhhhh!&#39; Sorry to swear, but, &#39;Motherfucker!&#39;” </p><figure id="attachment_3449353" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3449353" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3449353" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Jeremy-Strong-Succession-finale-main.jpg" alt="Succession finale" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Jeremy-Strong-Succession-finale-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Jeremy-Strong-Succession-finale-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Jeremy-Strong-Succession-finale-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Jeremy-Strong-Succession-finale-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Jeremy-Strong-Succession-finale-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Jeremy-Strong-Succession-finale-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3449353" class="wp-caption-text"> Jeremy Strong as Kendall Roy in the finale of &#39;Succession&#39;. CREDIT: HBO</figcaption></figure><p> In the series&#39; closing scenes, Shiv and Tom were seen holding hands in a car, but Snook didn&#39;t necessarily see that as a happy ending for her character.</p><p> “[Tom] would go into work the next day, and she would have to be dancing on outer rim,” she said. “Friends of mine have been like, &#39;So what do you think would happen to Shiv after this?&#39; Shiv is about to have a baby, all of this has gone down, she&#39;s sort of thrown back into a world with her husband that wasn&#39;t a great situation beforehand. But I think the baby thing is really about to hit in a way that is inescapable. And she&#39;s probably someone who would go into quite a deep postpartum depression, and quite a difficult next 12 months, I think.”</p><p> Snook also revealed that she only discovered <em>Succession</em> creator Jesse Armstrong was bringing the series to a close just moments before attending the show&#39;s last table read.</p><p> “I was understanding that it probably could end, but there were maybe mitigating factors that would maybe prevent it ending — which I won&#39;t go into,” she said. “But it could go one way or the other. And also, it&#39;s nice to hope.</p><p> She continued: “It was devastating. I didn&#39;t get a chance to finish the script before I got to the read-through. I was quickly devouring it in the car on the way there. And then by the time I finished, I just arrived and was like, &#39;That&#39;s it. It&#39;s done.&#39; And I walked in, and Matthew was like, &#39;No, I don&#39;t think so. I think that&#39;s quite hopeful! The last handhold, maybe there&#39;s potential for what&#39;s going to happen with Tom as CEO,&#39; or something like that.</p><p> “But then once we got into the room, Jesse made an announcement saying, &#39;Yeah. As you can see, this is the last.&#39;”</p><p> Elsewhere in the interview, Snook revealed that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/sarah-snook-reveals-succession-scene-that-was-cut-from-the-finale-3477221">the scene of Shiv returning to the boardroom to cast her vote against Kendall was cut from the show&#39;s finale</a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/succession-star-sarah-snook-explains-why-shiv-voted-against-kendall-3478313">&#39;Succession&#39; star Sarah Snook explains why Shiv voted against Kendall</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
